Package it.unimore.iot.health.api.datamanager.utils

package it.unimore.iot.health.api.datamanager.utils
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    DummyDataGenerator
    The DummyDataGenerator class is a utility class that can create patients and healthchecks in order to start the demo with already some patients and healthchecks to work with via the RESTful API.
    SenMLPack
    SenMLPack class represents a SenMLRecord ArrayList used for receiving telemetry data within MqttHandler and HealthCheckResource classes, and to emulate telemetry data within DummyDataGenerator
    SenMLRecord
    SenMLRecord class provides standardized structure for telemetry data
    UtilityClass
    UtilityClass is a helper class with only static methods that are useful in certain part of the codebase.
